nodes.text: Paqwepori was a small cluster of stars in the Mid Rim near the Corellian Run. It became a popular trading stop for spacers pushing into regions beyond the extent of the Galactic Republic centuries before the Battle of Yavin, driven by tales of bazaars and the antics of shopkeepers on Paqwepor Major.
The Paqwepori region contained almost ninety settled systems.
